author: joyce
msg: Resolved CLIMATE-17. Update bootstrap modals with animations.
- Changes open and close functions of bootstrap-modal over to native
bootstrap calls for open and close. This allows for a simpler
implementation at the expense of a bit of customizability (Which we
weren't using anyway). It also means we get animations with less code.
